# PWA access whitelist for oauth2-proxy.
#
# Copy this file to `oauth2-proxy-emails.txt` (same directory) and list the
# Google account emails allowed to sign in to the PWA — one per line.
# Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored by oauth2-proxy.
#
# To change who has access: edit oauth2-proxy-emails.txt and restart the
# proxy:  docker compose restart oauth2-proxy
#
# The real file is gitignored (it's your live allow-list); only this
# .example is tracked.

you@example.com
